93
00:10:45,391 --> 00:10:46,824
Fix what?

94
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:49,520
We'll give her a
normal funeral.

95
00:10:52,699 --> 00:10:55,668
We'll take care of her, then
I'll take care of you.

96
00:11:08,915 --> 00:11:10,883
Where are you going?

97
00:11:11,017 --> 00:11:13,178
