guilty for everything!

104
00:11:25,531 --> 00:11:27,226
I am not feeling guilty
about anything.

105
00:11:27,367 --> 00:11:29,858
Do you realize the significance of
what he just read?

106
00:11:30,036 --> 00:11:31,196
Well, she's gone!

107
00:11:31,337 --> 00:11:33,237
It's over, I'm at peace!

108
00:11:37,877 --> 00:11:40,004
I have fucking peace!

109
00:11:45,218 --> 00:11:47,243
I'm at peace now.

110
00:11:49,889 --> 00:11:51,516
Yes, I see.

111
00:11:55,795 --> 00:11:59,595
Mathematics as you
have known so far

112
00:11:59,732 --> 00:12:03,691
have aimed to achieve a precise
and definitive response

113
00:12:03,803 --> 00:12:06,738
to precise and definitive problems.

114
00:12:06,906 --> 00:12:10,364
Now, you are about to enter into
entirely different adventure.

115
00:12:10,476 --> 00:12:12,967
The subject will be
intractable problems

116
00:12:13,112 --> 00:12:14,704
