00:14:18,371 --> 00:14:20,931
You'll go knock on the
door Said Haidar

153
00:14:21,073 --> 00:14:23,507
an old friend of mine who
teaches at Daresh.

154
00:14:23,609 --> 00:14:25,543
You can trust him.

155
