think you're going?

175
00:20:30,709 --> 00:20:33,143
Nicolas, stop!

176
00:20:33,612 --> 00:20:34,738
Go back to your country.

177
00:20:35,981 --> 00:20:36,879
Wahab!

178
00:20:37,483 --> 00:20:40,543
